In Python 2.7.9, SSL certificate validation is enabled by default. This is a problem
for Splunk as we ship with a self-signed certificate. This patch merely sets it
back to the previous behavior. You can read more here:

https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0476/#opting-out

